Class Partitions

  • java.lang.Object
    • Partitions

  • public class Partitions
extends java.lang.Object
    The Partitions class generates all partitions of length less or equal to maxLength of positive integers less or equal to n. Partitions are written in the way in Caporaso-Harris' paper. i.e. if n = a1*1 + a2*2 + .... is a partition of n, then this partitions is recoreded as (a1, a2, ....).
    Since:
    August 27, 2019
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Yu-jong Tzeng
